FIG. 2 is a cross-sectional view showing the rear air-conditioning unit of the first embodiment of this invention;


FIG. 3 is a block diagram showing the control circuit for the servomotor in FIG. 2;


FIG. 4 is a graph showing drive characteristics of the servomotor in FIG. 2;


FIG. 5 is a descriptive drawing showing the link mechanism of the first embodiment of this invention and operating status during face mode;


FIG. 6 is a descriptive drawing of the link mechanism of FIG. 5 showing the operation status in foot mode and also at medium and high fan speeds;


FIG. 7 is a descriptive drawing of the link mechanism of FIG. 5 showing the operation status in foot mode and when fan speed is low;


FIGS. 8A-8C are drawings illustrating the operation of the rear air-conditioning unit shown in FIG. 2;


FIG. 9 is a cross sectional view showing the rear air-conditioning unit of a second preferred embodiment of the present invention; and


FIGS. 10A-10C are drawings illustrating the operation of the rear air-conditioning unit of the second embodiment.
